---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About - Enia">
  <main>
    <section class="intro fade-in">
      <h1>Legacy meets <span class="highlight">Singularity</span></h1>
      <p class="lead">From a mid-sized regional paper distributor to the world's leading provider of physical data substrates.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="history fade-in">
      <div class="timeline-item">
        <h3>1985</h3>
        <p>Founded as a traditional paper supply company in Scranton, PA. Focus: Customer service and limitless paper.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="timeline-item highlight-border">
        <h3>2024</h3>
        <p>Rebranded as Enia. We realized that paper isn't just wood pulpâ€”it's <strong>Analog Blockchain</strong>.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="team fade-in">
      <h2>The Neural Network (Team)</h2>
      <div class="grid">
        <div class="member">
          <div class="placeholder-img"></div>
          <h3>Michael S.</h3>
          <p class="role">Chief Inspiration Officer</p>
          <p class="desc">"Would I rather be feared or loved? Easy. Both. I want people to be afraid of how much they love our paper."</p>
        </div>
        <div class="member">
          <div class="placeholder-img"></div>
          <h3>Dwight S.</h3>
          <p class="role">Assistant to the Regional Algorithm</p>
          <p class="desc">"Paper is the most resilient storage medium. Bears can't hack paper. Beets are irrelevant."</p>
        </div>
        <div class="member">
          <div class="placeholder-img"></div>
          <h3>Jim H.</h3>
          <p class="role">Head of Pranks & UX</p>
          <p class="desc">"I put the AI in 'Wait, what?'"</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  main {
    max-width: 1000px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 10rem 2rem 6rem;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .intro {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 6rem;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: 3.5rem;
  }

  .highlight {
    color: var(--color-primary);
  }

  .highlight-border {
    border-color: var(--color-primary) !important;
  }

  .lead {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: rgba(224, 224, 224, 0.8);
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 1rem auto;
  }

  .history {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 6rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  .history::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 20px;
    top: 0;
    height: 100%;
    width: 2px;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
  }

  .timeline-item {
    margin-left: 3rem;
    padding: 2rem;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
    border-left: 2px solid transparent;
    border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
  }

  .team h2 {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    color: var(--color-secondary);
  }

  .grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .member {
    background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    padding: 2rem;
    text-align: center;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
  }

  .member:hover {
    transform: translateY(-10px);
    border-color: var(--color-secondary);
  }

  .placeholder-img {
    width: 100px;
    height: 100px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-primary), var(--color-secondary));
    border-radius: 50%;
    margin: 0 auto 1.5rem;
    opacity: 0.8;
  }

  .role {
    color: var(--color-primary);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
  }

  .desc {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-style: italic;
    opacity: 0.7;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    h1 { font-size: 2.5rem; } 
  }
</style>
